Description: YouTube is a video hosting and sharing website created in February 2005 and acquired by Google in November 2006.
Flickr is an image and video hosting and sharing website acquired by Yahoo in 2005, and now owned by Oath.

Instagram is an online mobile photo-sharing site that allows users to share pictures and videos either publicly or privately on the app, as well as through a variety of other social networking platforms. It was acquired by Facebook in 2012.
Periscope is a live video streaming mobile app acquired by Twitter in 2015. In December 2016, some of Periscope's features were integrated into the main Twitter app.
